-- Telkom Chairman Says Hedberg Is Being Considered for Chief Executive Post
-- Nicky Smith
-- 2010-07-28T06:20:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/telkom-chairman-says-hedberg-is-being-considered-for-chief-executive-post.html

          
          
             Telkom South Africa Ltd. Chairman
Jeff Molobela said acting Chief Executive Officer Jeffrey
Hedberg is being considered for the CEO post.  
 Molobela made the comments to reporters in Johannesburg
today.  
